# ─── Azure Blob Storage (optional — for server-side file storage) ────────────
# Set these in Supabase Edge Function secrets (NOT in browser env vars):
#   AZURE_STORAGE_ACCOUNT=<storage account name>
#   AZURE_STORAGE_KEY=<storage account key>
#   AZURE_STORAGE_CONTAINER=one-dsd-files
# If not set, Edge Functions fall back to Supabase Storage automatically.

# ─── Cloud deployment notes ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Lovable:  set vars in Project → Settings → Environment Variables
# Azure SWA: set vars in Azure Portal → Static Web App → Configuration
# Netlify:  set vars in Site → Site configuration → Environment variables
# Vercel:   set vars in Project → Settings → Environment Variables
#
# NEVER commit .env or .env.local — this .env.example is safe to commit.
